          <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">bacteria</ENAMEX> are adherent, as <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">InlA</ENAMEX> expression is only partly
          dependent on <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">PrfA</ENAMEX> [ <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">46</TIMEX>]. No actin <ENAMEX TYPE="FAC_DESC">structures</ENAMEX> were seen in
          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">association</ENAMEX> with these <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">bacteria</ENAMEX>, implying that they were
